g/resource/Michal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The top 8 finishers advance to the Olympic finals, which means only Krzysztof will compete in the final.\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic final will take place in the Paris La D\\u00c3\\u00a9fense Arena.\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was scheduled for July 31 at 11:37 am PT but has been rescheduled.\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chmielewski will also compete in the semifinals for the 1500-meter freestyle in the second heat on August 3.\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1864, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Similarly to the 200-meter butterfly seminfinal, only the top 8 finishers will advance to the final.\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 1965, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He is ranked eighth in his heat with an entry time of 15.01.89.\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 2029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is unlikely Chmielewski will advance to the 1500-meter freestyle final as he is ranked 24th overall.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"More USC:Eric Musselman Offers Rave Review for Hall of Fame LA Great  Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2231, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2140, \"end\": 2143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USC_Trojans\", \"score\": 0.9999999986946477, \"rank\": 1.3043677183580493e-09, \"text\": \"USC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USC_Trojans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USC_Trojans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations  Samantha Garcia is a student at the University of California, Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2305, \"end\": 2311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Garcia\", \"score\": 0.9999999950375695, \"rank\": 4.96193224772663e-09